     <!--mainbar begin--> 
     <div id="con">
      <!--内容--> 
      <h3><span><em><font style=" font-weight:normal ;font-style:normal; color:">临泉县村级收支票据管理办法</font></em></span> </h3> 
      <div class="box"> 
       <!--相关信息--> 
       <div class="info">
        录入：田桥乡 | 作者：田桥乡 | 日期：2013-10-15 00:00:00 | 浏览
        <font color="red"> 3</font> 次
       </div> 
       <!--正文--> 
       <div id="fontzoom" class="content"> 
        <div id="articleContnet"> 
         <div id="zoom"> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 0703">为进一步加强村级资金收支管理，规范使用</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">村级收支票据</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 0703">，充分发挥乡镇农村集体“三资”委托代理服务中心监管职能，确保有限的村级资金更好地为农村经济</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">社会发展服务，特制定本管理办法。<span lang="EN-US">
             <!--?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /-->
             <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align="left"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">一、规范使用统一收支票据。</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">各村对内对外收取款项及往来结算业务，统一使用县推进“阳光村务工程”建设工作领导小组办公室印制的村级收入和支出专用票据，其他非正规票据一律不得使用。对不使用规定票据或私制票据的，</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 0703">将</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">严肃查处。<span lang="EN-US">
             <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align="left"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">二、合理有序发放收支票据。</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 0703">乡镇农村集体“三资”委托代理服务中心负责票据统一申请和领取，并发放到村。</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">县推进“阳光村务工程”建设工作领导小组办公室本次发放收支票据三种，每村共<font face="仿宋_GB2312"><span lang="EN-US"><font size="5">35</font></span>本，包括村级财务专项资金支取申请书<span lang="EN-US"><font size="5">5</font></span>本、村级收入专用票据<span lang="EN-US"><font size="5">15</font></span>本、村级支出专用票据<span lang="EN-US"><font size="5">15</font></span>本。<span lang="EN-US">
              <o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align="left"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">三、严格收支票据管理程序。</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">建立票据领用登记和销号制度，由县推进“阳光村务工程”建设工作领导小组办公室建立收支票据管理台帐，对领取的收支票据造册登记。村报帐员首次领取三种票据各一本，由</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 0703">乡镇农村集体“三资”委托代理服务中心</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">按日期、编号、起讫号码逐本登记；村报帐员使用完一本票据后，凭完整的编号存根联票据（作废票据应三联完备）继续领取相关票据。对村报帐员交回的票据，</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 0703">乡镇农村集体“三资”委托代理服务中心</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">应逐笔销号，并收回归档备查。<span lang="EN-US">
             <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32.15pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align="left"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">四、加大收支票据监管力度。</span></b><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">主要是审核收支票据填写内容是否规范，金额大小写是否一致，经手人、负责人的签字和村公章、村监委审核盖章是否齐全等，尤其要审核票据的存根联与记帐联的书写内容、笔迹是否一致，有无复写的印迹，保证内容真实，数据相符。<span lang="EN-US">
             <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 26pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" align="left"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">
            <o:p>
             &nbsp;
            </o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 176pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 11.0" align="left"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">临泉县推进“阳光村务工程”<span lang="EN-US">
             <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 176pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 28pt; TEXT-ALIGN: left; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 10.0" align="left"><span style="text-fit: 192.0pt; mso-text-fit-id: -194247424"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; LETTER-SPACING: 0.8pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">建设工作领导小组办公室</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">
            <o:p></o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt"><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">
            <o:p>
             &nbsp;
            </o:p></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; TEXT-INDENT: 192pt; mso-char-indent-count: 12.0"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体">二<span lang="EN-US"><font size="5">0</font></span>一一年四月十二日<span lang="EN-US">
             <o:p></o:p></span></span></p> 
          <p class="MsoNormal" style="BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 6pt 0cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-pagination: widow-orphan" align="center"><b><span lang="EN-US" style="FONT-SIZE: 22pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 180%; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体">
             <o:p>
              &nbsp;
             </o:p></span></b></p> 
         </div> 
